profile:
Mavriq Construction is a general contractor specializing in home renovations in Thunder Bay and surrounding areas. Our proven design process has helped our clients turn their vision into concrete designs. A customer’s habits, aesthetic tastes and functional requirements help drive the technical design and ensure the customer ends up with a product that they will love for years to come.

Our Employees have years of experience and knowledge in their respective fields. We hire with an eye for employees that find reward in quality handiwork and strive for continual improvement. We constantly develop our processes to deliver top quality service.

Services:
- General Contracting
- General Carpentry
- Soffit, facia and eavestrough
- Door and Window Capping
- Metal Roofing
- Laminate, Hardwood and Vinyl Flooring
- Windows and Doors
- Decks and Fences
- Custom and Stock Cabinetry
- Tiling
- Drywall
- Painting
- Etc.

See our website for more details
